stories.title: South Africa hit their straps to crush Sri Lanka in second ODI
stories.summary: With an utterly charming Neil McKenzie century as the cornerstone, South Africa produced their best one-day performance of the summer to crush Sri Lanka by 95 runs in the second game of the Standard Bank Series at Buffalo Park on Sunday
